Privacy Policy

This Privacy Policy explains how your personal information is collected, used, and disclosed by Ghoshpukur College. By using the Ghoshpukur College app, you consent to the data practices described in this policy.

Information Collection and Use

The Ghoshpukur College app requires access to your Google account for login purposes. We collect your name, email address, and profile picture associated with your Google account to provide you with a personalized experience on the app. We do not store your Google account password.

We also collect certain usage data, such as the pages you visit, the date and time of your visit, and the files you download. This information is used to improve the app's functionality and provide better service to our users.

Information Sharing and Disclosure

We do not share your personal information with third parties, except as required by law or to comply with a legal process. We may share anonymized usage data with third parties for analytics and research purposes.

Security

We take reasonable measures to protect your personal information from unauthorized access, alteration, or disclosure. We use SSL encryption to protect your data during transmission, and we store your data on secure servers.

Your Rights

You have the right to access, modify, and delete your personal information collected by Ghoshpukur College. You may also opt-out of certain data collection practices by adjusting the app's settings.

Changes to this Privacy Policy

We reserve the right to update this privacy policy from time to time. We will notify you of any significant changes to this policy by email or by posting a notice on the app.

Contact Us

If you have any questions about this privacy policy or the app's data practices, please contact us at [ghoshpukurcollege@gmail.com].
